Metadata: StreamWebs Student Stewardship Network: Final Report (NOAA B-WET Program)

This report summarizes the StreamWebs program, curriculum development and testing. The StreamWebs program provided students, teachers and project partners with hands-on field and classroom trainings; access to field sampling equipment; curriculum materials and open-source, web-based tools for watershed data analysis. The program launched a number of new partnerships and added to the exisiting cohort of teachers and community partners.
